I'm a no-vote for now. This feels like a generic thing that traps you forever, and produces weird media as well to me, with a somewhat thin veneer of film festival put over it. I think if you intensified the effect or did more with the horror of being trapped in it, it would work better. Right now, there isn't a lot that makes it stand out from similar SCPs.







