This is a totally valid critique, thanks for sharing. This is my first  SCP and my main goal was to capture the spirit of classic SCPs that I love with my own original take on an anomaly. I agree that it's not particularly original, but that's sort of a consequence of what I was aiming for.

I agree that it could be more fleshed out though. I'm hoping to bring more originality and depth to my future articles! Thanks so much for reading and sharing your opinion!







